name: Taupō
description: Key lime, spanish cedar, and freshly zested orange. Medium straw hue, meringue-like foam.   Riwaka, Wakatu, Citra

name: Tides
description: Citrus, passionfruit and cantaloupe. Blueberry aroma. El Dorado, Citra, Mosaic, Simcoe

name: Drip
description: White grape, grapefruit and orange.  Phantasm, Motueka, Nelson Sauvin, Citra

name: Lupula
description: Pineapple, mango, and ruby red grapefruit. Aromatic.   Riwaka, Moutere, Motueka, Comet

name: Scylla
description: Dark chocolate and toasted caramel layered on blackberry cola.

name: Zama
description: Pineapple, tangerine, mango.   Nectaron, El Dorado, Ekuanot

name: Grandar
description: Light bready sweetness balanced by hops, floral and herbal notes that finish with a subtle citrus. Step mashed and hopped with Hallertauer Mittelfrüh and Saaz.

name: Terra
description: Orange zest, marmalade, and grapefruit. Floral and spicy.   Wakatu, Motueka

name: Solem
description: Bold pineapple, leather, and ripe peach.
